WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:02.320
Previously on "Timeless"...

00:02.323 --> 00:03.961
- Help!
- That's why we're here.

00:03.965 --> 00:05.129
To save his life.

00:05.130 --> 00:06.997
His name is Nicholas Keynes.

00:07.000 --> 00:09.175
- Where am I?
- You're with Rittenhouse.

00:09.176 --> 00:11.220
In the year 2018.

00:11.223 --> 00:13.638
- And who are you?
- I'm your granddaughter.

00:13.639 --> 00:14.820
Your mother's Rittenhouse?

00:14.823 --> 00:17.504
You have come so far
these past few weeks, Lucy.

00:17.507 --> 00:18.554
I'm proud of you.

00:18.557 --> 00:20.224
Be with us, be on the
right side of history.

00:20.226 --> 00:22.231
This is so much bigger than you or me.

00:22.234 --> 00:24.334
Mom.

00:24.336 --> 00:26.069
Mom!

00:27.706 --> 00:29.439
Jiya.

00:29.441 --> 00:32.042
The mother ship visited
ten different destinations.

00:32.043 --> 00:34.311
History could've changed
and we wouldn't even know it.

00:34.313 --> 00:36.079
I've been reading these plans they have.

00:36.081 --> 00:38.248
Key moments in history
to change the present.

00:38.250 --> 00:40.417
The captain, 1918, he worked
his way up through the ranks.

00:40.419 --> 00:42.585
Emma, she'd been in the
late 1800s for ten years.

00:42.587 --> 00:44.013
I mean, what if they've already planted

00:44.015 --> 00:45.655
who knows how many agents in history?

00:45.657 --> 00:47.700
Was there anything in there
about a Nicholas Keynes?

00:47.703 --> 00:51.027
These plans, this manifesto,
Nicholas Keynes wrote it.

00:51.029 --> 00:53.906
- Something's happened.
- I'll only talk to Lucy.

00:55.000 --> 01:01.074
